   [healtiptxt.gif] Understand Cholesterol... At Last

   We've been bombarded with so much complicated and conflicting
   information about cholesterol that it makes the head spin. But before
   you throw up your hands in disgust and dig into a
   four-egg-bacon-cheese-omelet with fries on the side, read this. It's
   important to understand how cholesterol and fat affect your health.

   See CalPERS Health Pages for more information.
